724
01:19:39,071 --> 01:19:42,366
Mr. Cole, you really are an enigma.

725
01:19:42,491 --> 01:19:46,328
So which are you, and
artist or a writer?

726
01:19:46,370 --> 01:19:48,956
Oh, Glorie, I'm...

727
01:19:49,039 --> 01:19:52,835
I'm neither, really. I'm... I'm
