740
01:22:31,910 --> 01:22:34,955
- So you were at the doctor's office
getting the stitches taken out? - Uh-huh.

741
01:22:34,997 --> 01:22:38,000
And we went to the
beach. And we had lunch.

742
01:22:38,000 --> 01:22:41,295
And Eddie showed me my fingerprint.
Oh, that's really neat, Ruth.

743
01:22:41,378 --> 01:22:44,965
- I see the photograph was ready finally.
- We got the feet back!

744
01:22:45,007 --> 01:22:48,594
Look at all this sand in your hair,
Ruth. You're gonna need a bath.

745
01:22:48,635 --> 01:22:54,600
Well, I was waiting quite a while
for you this morning. Where were ya?

746
01:22:55,726 --> 01:22:58,312
Where's Marion going? I'll give
her the bath. Better read that.

747
01:22:58,395 --> 01:23:00,856
- Answer me.
- Read that first.

748
01:23:00,898 --> 01:23:04,484
What's this? It's the only good
writing I've done all summer.

749
01:23:08,197 --> 01:23:10,199
"60 times"?

750
01:23:16,288 --> 01:23:18,290
Okay. Let's run.

751
01:23:22,878 --> 01:23:24,755
Did you saw that?

752
01:23:24,880 --> 01:23:30,385
Where are all the other pictures? Uh,
I don't know. Maybe Mommy moved them.

753
01:23:30,511 --> 01:23:36,433
Look at you. You've got sand in your toes and in
