754
01:23:36,517 --> 01:23:39,353
Well, I guess it's a
good time for a bath then.

755
01:23:41,104 --> 01:23:45,651
But Mommy didn't move those
things. What are those things?

756
01:23:45,692 --> 01:23:48,070
They're picture hooks.

757
01:23:49,947 --> 01:23:54,034
- Mommy moved all the pictures but not the picture hooks.
- I'll give Ruth the bath.

758
01:23:54,076 --> 01:23:57,037
I'll take a quick shower.
Yeah. Make it quick.

759
01:23:59,081 --> 01:24:01,542
Why would Mommy do that?

760
01:24:03,418 --> 01:24:05,963
I don't know, sweetie.

761
01:24:11,552 --> 01:24:14,972
Hi. This is Ted. I
can't play today, Dave.

762
01:24:15,097 --> 01:24:17,099
Yeah, my wife's left me.

763
01:24:18,183 --> 01:24:21,395
No, no. I'm okay.

764
01:24:24,565 --> 01:24:27,025
Yeah. All right. Yeah.

765
01:24:27,109 --> 01:24:30,696
I'll see you then. Bye.

766
01:24:35,284 --> 01:24:37,411
Aah! Where the fuck is my wife?

767
01:24:37,536 --> 01:24:39,538
I don't know. Don't lie to me.

768
01:24:42,124 --> 01:24:45,586
Jesus!

769
01:24:45,586 --> 01:24:47,588
Christ!

770
01:24:47,588 --> 01:24:50,591
I hit you with an open hand...
with the flat of my hand!

771
01:24:50,632 --> 01:24:53,010
You clench your fist, you
punch me in the nose? I'm sorry.

772
01:24:53,135 --> 01:24:55,971
Jesus Christ.! I'm sorry. Marion
said it was gonna make you stop.

773
01:24:56,013 --> 01:24:59,433
"Marion said"? If she thinks she's
got a rat's ass of a chance...

774
01:24:59,433 --> 01:25:02,186
to get custody of Ruth, she's
got another think coming.

775
01:25:02,269 --> 01:25:06,690
She doesn't expect to get custody of
Ruth. She has no intention of trying.

776
01:25:06,732 --> 01:25:12,154
- She told you that?
- "She told me everything I'm telling you."

777
01:25:14,823 --> 01:25:20,746
What kind of mother doesn't even
